  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Labour standards in the leather value chain</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The overall purpose of this project is to improve working conditions and reduce labour rights abuses by promoting adherence to international labour standards (ILS) and corporate social responsibility (CSR) in leather-based, garment, footwear and accessories value chains. To be achieved through increased commitment by private sector and government stakeholders to fulfil their due diligence obligations with a focus on leather production hubs in India, Pakistan and Bangladesh.</narrative>
